    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i've been trying to get a sourdough starter going for like a week now but im stuck. i fed it yesterday with some unbleached bread flour and water but it hasn't really grown or bubbled at all after 24 hours. my kitchen is around 68 degrees usually. am i doing something wrong?",
