    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the tip. i'll try moving it to a warmer spot tonight. i was also wondering if the type of flour matters? i'm just using standard bread flour right now, but i saw someone online saying rye or whole wheat might make it bubble faster because of more nutrients or something. does that actually make a difference or is it just hype?",
